find the lenght of the last word in the sentence

program:

def length_of_last_word(sentence):
    words = sentence.split()
    if words:
        return len(words[-1])
    return 0
sentence = "lahari venkatesh"
length = length_of_last_word(sentence)
print(f"The length of the last word in the sentence is: {length}")


output:
the no letters in last word is = 8
